###
Ministerial order
MINISTERIAL ORDER N° 006/2016 OF 08/01/2016 DETERMINING CURRICULUM, TEACHING HOURS AND THE LANGUAGE OF INSTRUCTION IN PRIMARY, SECONDARY AND SPECIALIZED SCHOOLS
The Minister of Education; Pursuant to the Constitution of the Republic of Rwanda of 2003 as revised in 2015, especially in Articles 121, 122 and 176; Pursuant to Law n° 23/2012 of 15/06/2012 governing organization and functioning of nursery, primary and secondary education, especially in Articles 35, 40 and 46; After consideration and approval by the cabinet, in its session of 14/05/2015; HEREBY ORDERS: